  "2380070": {
    "name": "Slime Squadron: Harpy Raiders",
    "steam_appid": 2380070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/c036e3733c7fd84ccee24c5e3ead4ba5.avif?t=1759321758\" width=472 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slide and stretch your slime squadrons to victory in daring raids against the Harpy Empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For too long, slimekind has been seen as a pushover by its myriad of multi-limbed foes. Now, the perfidious harpy race seeks to humiliate us in front of the entire world. Would we stand idly by and see these squawkers smugly triumph?</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An <strong>RPG-Platformer</strong> which combines the 4 member party format with fast paced side-scroller action.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Elaborate storytelling</strong> but <i>without</i> the walls of text! (Mostly!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the <strong>grappling hook</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/b4b55d5f49e85bf32180261fcc34c5f3.poster.avif?t=1759321758\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/b4b55d5f49e85bf32180261fcc34c5f3.webm?t=1759321758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/b4b55d5f49e85bf32180261fcc34c5f3.mp4?t=1759321758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/dd20254c096fbd8a1598ce93759cff9f.avif?t=1759321758\" width=472 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Our enemies are as plenty as they are tough. But where they see us as puny, every slime knows that our strength is in numbers. Build your squad and sacrifice their lives as necessary - its what they were conscripted signed up for!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slimes do not wear armor. But you can <strong>mutate</strong> them to become their own armor, or maybe they'll just explode. It's a real bargain!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raid the secondary floating islands to gain ever <strong>stronger weapons</strong> and loot!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/d97c2f192b2a366ff8e310e424d53c9f.poster.avif?t=1759321758\" width=1062 height=708 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/d97c2f192b2a366ff8e310e424d53c9f.webm?t=1759321758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/d97c2f192b2a366ff8e310e424d53c9f.mp4?t=1759321758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/233a0317e26d09bcba3181b7de4ce754.avif?t=1759321758\" width=472 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take the fight to the countless sky islands - some widely-known and well-mapped as strongholds of the Empire, while countless others are as ephemeral as the wind and seemingly as random.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slime Army High Command has identified roughly <strong>10 major missions</strong> that requires your attention, and there is little time to waste.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight insane bosses</strong>, and lay waste to the enemies of slimekind with the might of the modern military!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/b870fba55d44a695fe362efc2217559f.poster.avif?t=1759321758\" width=1026 height=552 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/b870fba55d44a695fe362efc2217559f.webm?t=1759321758\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/b870fba55d44a695fe362efc2217559f.mp4?t=1759321758\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/632581805ccd6a0851b3546bd230592a.avif?t=1759321758\" width=472 height=89 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choices matter.</strong> Balance the slime masses' clamoring for vengeance against the ever-watching judgment of the hardly sympathetic international media.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But also, harpies are by nature <strong>dumb, arrogant and evil</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Good soldiers do not question.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2380070/extras/372c5fcde9c0ea054f191526a052f5fd.avif?t=1759321758\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p></li></ul>",
